description.plain:
“Car Crash in G Major” was written while Judge was experiencing a severe flare up of Crohn’s Disease, leaving them bedridden in their childhood home for 10 months.

“[Car Crash in G Major]’s about taking the good with the bad,” says Judge. “You can’t really appreciate one without the other.”
